message: Would you be interested in a unicorn dance party on Saturday night? Not 100% sure I’m going yet but I LOVE unicorns! It’s at house of yes.
Mine would be pride week in ny. I like the spirit of radical acceptance.
What are your other favorite weeks of the year?
I’m really excited for it! Yea, I have everything planned out. The people I’m going with a super into it and have been going for years. I find the comforting. It’s a lot.
That’s awesome. I hope you have an amazing time. Burning man is one of my favorite weeks of the year. Are you sleeping in a tent? Do you have a shade structure at your camp?

I’ve never been before. I’m going with Burning Man Inc (mutual friends are part of the founders) so I’m going with them. They do the Sonic Runway art piece. I really wanted to get an RV but it is so much extra work I didn’t do it.

I used to live in SF. I love haight too.

Is this your first time at burning man? Who are you camping with? I used to camp with mooncheese before RV camping a couple times. I’m going with Black Lotus this year. 

That’s incredibly misleading. I keep my sailboat at pier 40, off W. Houston. Its moored, but it’s within walking distance of my office and my apartment. 

Good luck on your matches tonight.
I love sailing! I actually just got certified. Ha! Where do you keep your sailboat? I was looking at joining the Manhattan Yacht Club but it’s out in Jersey. Very misleading name.

Tonight I’m playing at Kingston Hall. My league has never played out of Amsterdam but I go sometimes bc I live close by. There’s a lot of very solid players there so it’s kind of a pool “scene” place. I was in San Fran for the weekend to visit friends. Haight Street was by far my favorite place. I was able to gather inspiration for my costume for Burning Man end of Aug.

Hi! That’s an incredibly kind and thoughtful offer. Thank you for thinking of me. Are you playing at Amsterdam billiards? I’ve walked by that place so many times and I’ve always wanted to go in. I love playing pool but I’m not very good at it. Unfortunately, I can’t tonight. I went away over the weekend as well and I have too much to catch up on at work. I’m free every other day this week (except saturday afternoon). Can I join for pool next week or would you like to try something else this week? If you like sailing, we could take my sailboat out. 

Where were you in California and how was California?

I’m in California this weekend, getting back on Monday. I am in a pool league on Monday that plays in the East Village. We could  plan to get food before and you are welcome to come to pool afterward. Interested?
I’m pretty sure that most/all the dinosaurs had feathers. I’ve never looked at a bird the same way after finding that out. Jurassic Park needs to be updated, we’ve been lied to!
Some dinosaurs had feathers! Parts of the world that dinosaurs roamed around in were cold. I don't mind. How do you feel about feathers?
How did you feel about dinosaurs having feathers?
Wrong. He speaks 12. Very close though
2 truths and a lie. My grandfather can speak 11 languages fluently. I taught my goldfish to swim through a hoop. My family adopted a homeless man that went on to make over a quarter million a year.
